		<td><b>Doing 14x16 square tiles is possible</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<img src="./download/file.php?id=12943" alt="aspect ratio corrected tiles.png" /><br />
			<span class="gensmall">aspect ratio corrected tiles.png [ 1.41 KiB | Viewed 1092 times ]</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br /><br />You could pull off 14x16 tiles by overlapping 2 layers, and using 2 tile sets.  As you can see in the picture above, there is a red layer and a green layer.  Each tile comes in a pair, with a &quot;right&quot; side tile, and a &quot;left&quot; side tile.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
